---
title: One-Pot Beef Meatball Ragu & Penne with Silverbeet & Parmesan Cheese
description: Rich, radiant and ravishing to eat, do we need to say any more about this beef ragu? Stir through a mixture of veggies including carrot and spinach. Cook everything up in one pot with the penne and your ragu is ready!

*Unfortunately, this
week's fusilli was in
short supply, so we've
replaced it with penne.
Don't worry, the recipe
will be just as delicious,
just be sure to follow
your recipe card!*
